HEADWORD: Milliard
<hw>Mil`liard"</hw> <pr>(F. m⟦esl⟧l`y⟦adot⟧r"; E.
m⟦icr⟧l"l⟦icr⟧*⟦aum⟧rd)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., from
<ets>mille</ets>, <ets>mil</ets>, thousand, L. <ets>mille</ets>.]</ety>
<def>A thousand millions; -- usually called <altname>billion</altname>
in the United States. See <er>Billion</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

